oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 4
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." This is part four of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is the eighteenth of an unidentified number of tapes.
